                        <interp inst="t18361128-name-640" type="given" value="HENRY"></interp>HENRY HUGGINS</persName>
                  </hi>. I said there was a mark on the corner with both or one of my initials, and there is the letter H on it.</p>
               <p>(The prisoner Kidd received a good character.)</p>
